      "type": "title",
      "source": "🔬 Deep Focus Mode",
      "target": "🔬 深度专注模式"
    },
    {
      "type": "description",
      "source": "Science-backed single-switch mode — sepia/warm-dark palette, neutral headings, flattened chrome, 68ch measure. Overrides any active season palette.",
      "target": "基于科学的单开关模式——棕褐色/暖色调深色方案，中性标题，扁平化界面，68字符行宽。会覆盖任何活动的季节配色方案。"
    },
    {
      "type": "title",
      "source": "Enable Deep Focus Mode",
      "target": "启用深度专注模式"
    },
    {
      "type": "description",
      "source": "Activates warm sepia (light) or warm dark (dark) palette, collapses heading colour hierarchy, kills decorative backgrounds and animations, and hides the ribbon and status bar. Overrides whatever season is active.",
      "target": "激活暖棕褐色（浅色）或暖深色（深色）方案，折叠标题颜色层级，移除装饰性背景和动画，并隐藏功能区和状态栏。会覆盖当前活动的季节。"
    },
    {
      "type": "title",
      "source": "Typewriter Dimming",
      "target": "打字机淡出效果"
    },
    {
      "type": "description",
      "source": "Fade non-active lines to ~50% opacity in live-preview (iA Writer style). Reading mode dims all paragraphs until hovered.",
      "target": "在实时预览中，将非活动行淡出至约50%不透明度（iA Writer风格）。阅读模式下，所有段落会在悬停前淡出。"
    },
    {
      "type": "title",
      "source": "Hide Sidebar Panels",
      "target": "隐藏侧边栏面板"
    },
    {
      "type": "description",
      "source": "Collapse the left and right sidebar content panels so only the editor canvas is visible.",
      "target": "折叠左右侧边栏内容面板，仅显示编辑器画布。"
    },
    {
      "type": "title",
      "source": "Keep Ribbon & Status Bar",
      "target": "保留功能区和状态栏"
    },
    {
      "type": "description",
      "source": "Escape hatch — show ribbon and status bar even in Focus Mode. Palette and heading neutralisation remain active.",
      "target": "逃生通道——即使在专注模式下也显示功能区和状态栏。调色板和标题中性化设置保持活动。"
    },
